injuries.comment: The Maple Leafs announced that Muzzin has been ruled out for the rest of the season.
The Toronto Maple Leafs placed D Victor Mete on injured reserve.
The Maple Leafs announced that Robertson underwent surgery and will be out for six months.
Hornqvist is not expected to return this season, David Dwork of Local 10 Miami reports.
Gudas left and was ruled out for the remainder of Monday's (Jun. 5) game against Vegas.
Luostarinen did not play in Monday's game (June 5).
The Montreal Canadiens placed F Paul Byron on long term injured reserve.
Canadiens GM Kent Hughes said he doesn't see Price playing during the 2022-23 season.
The Carolina Hurricanes placed F Max Pacioretty on injured reserve with a torn achilles tendon. He is OUT until at least April 13th per cbssports.com
The Carolina Hurricanes placed D Jake Gardiner on long-term injured reserve as he continues to recover from hip and back surgeries.
The Carolina Hurricanes placed F Andrei Svechnikov on injured reserve.
The Carolina Hurricanes placed F Ondrej Kase on injured reserve. He will be OUT until at least March 7th per cbssports.com
The New Jersey Devils placed G Jonathan Bernier on long-term injured reserve as he recovers from right hip surgery.
Hamilton had surgery and is expected to be ready at the start of next season.
Patrick Kane will be shelved four to six months after undergoing a hip resurfacing procedure, his agent said Thursday.
The Islanders announced that Wahlstrom is out for the season.
The Avalanche announced that Landeskog is undergoing surgery and is expected to miss the entire 2023-24 season.
Avalanche coach Jared Bednar said Cogliano has a neck fracture and is out for the remainder of the postseason.
Francouz had an adductor procedure following Colorado's first-round playoff exit.
Lehkonen suffered a broken toe during Colorado's first-round playoff series against Seattle.
The Wild announced that Shaw suffered a torn ACL.
The Winnipeg Jets placed F Sam Gagner on injured reserve.
The Golden Knights traded Weber's contract and a 2023 fifth-round pick to the Arizona Coyotes in exchange for Dysin Mayo, Kevin Weekes of ESPN reports.
Voracek is not expected to resume his NHL career, Aaron Portzline of The Athletic reports
Brossoit hasn't resumed skating and may not be an option during Vegas' series against Dallas, according to Ben Gotz of the Las Vegas Review-Journal.
Thompson (lower body) hasn't resumed skating yet, Ben Gotz of the Las Vegas Review-Journal reports.
The Golden Knights said Lehner is expected to miss the 2022-23 season.
The Vegas Golden Knights placed F Nolan Patrick on the long-term injured reserve list.
Karlsson missed Wednesday's practice because of an illness, according to Ben Gotz of the Las Vegas Review-Journal.
The Edmonton Oilers placed D Ryan Murray on injured reserve.
The Edmonton Oilers placed G Mike Smith on injured reserve.
Oilers GM Ken Holland said Klefbom isn't expecting to play again.
The Seattle Kraken placed F Joonas Donskoi on injured reserve.
